text: Jay Wilson Weatherill (born 3 April 1964) is an Australian politician. He was the 45th Premier of South Australia from 21 October 2011 to 19 March 2018, from the Labor Party. == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Australian Anglicans Category:Australian Labor Party politicians Category:Australian lawyers Category:Politicians from Adelaide Category:Premiers of South Australia
